{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I look up and it says, Arbeit-- whatever is the other thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never was good in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened is we go in and they leave us there, back of the gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They open the gate where the German guard is guarding it and we go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we see that on both side-- no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On one side, on the-- on the right side-- when you walk in on the right side, that there is like a small brick building.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of girls are standing on line front of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Meantime, I see that on the other side, where the mans were, that I hear the music and they are playing the music, the most beautiful music just like the-- the German soldiers who were selecting us at [INAUDIBLE], he was singing 'The Merry Widow' and he was swinging his bat.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now the same thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a group of people there who were in a-- in a stage sort of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were wearing black tuxedos and they were-- they were playing all different beautiful music.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the people started to march, all the men with the little belt on them and the bucket attached to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were all marching, marching, marching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was no end to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I seen that there were this tall, beautiful Gypsy womans walking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had-- on their head they had like these woven baskets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then on the right, there was a barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I see that very well-dressed, very heavy rouged girls were coming, going, laughing, and they were-- I said to my sister, we are in a-- in a crazy place.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I've never seen such a things like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we are standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
